                            <comment id="81448" author="yong.fan" created="Fri, 11 Apr 2014 19:00:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is another failure instance of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4879&quot; title=&quot;sanity-lfsck test 17 failure: test_17 failed with 3 &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4879&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4879&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="81443" author="jamesanunez" created="Fri, 11 Apr 2014 18:44:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Note that there are other test 18d failures that have the same error message, but the status after 32 seconds is &quot;scanning-phase2&quot;; &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d1a9ae82-ab04-11e3-bd80-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d1a9ae82-ab04-11e3-bd80-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e4b24d3e-b7f9-11e3-987f-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e4b24d3e-b7f9-11e3-987f-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt; . &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For these cases, we may just need to increase the wait time for LFSCK to complete.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
